'''惠特利灣'''（Whitley Bay）是位於[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]東北海岸的一座海濱小鎮，在歷史上屬於[[諾森伯蘭|諾森伯蘭]]，現在是[[泰恩-威爾郡|泰恩-威爾郡]]的一部分。惠特利灣首次被提到是在1100年。2006年BBC情境喜劇Thin Ice在這裡拍攝<ref>{{Cite web|title = British Comedy Guide - Thin Ice|url = http://www.sitcom.co.uk/thin_ice/|website = www.sitcom.co.uk|accessdate = 2015-10-12|archive-date = 2015-08-10|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150810053445/http://www.sitcom.co.uk/thin_ice/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/news/local-news/sophie-delighted-to-be-on-thin-ice-1026084|title=Sophie delighted to be on Thin Ice|date=29 August 2007|work=Manchester Evening News|accessdate=2016-03-04|archive-date=2019-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191201005442/https://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/news/local-news/sophie-delighted-to-be-on-thin-ice-1026084|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
